Firecos Module Patch

Patches that make the Firedocs module work with the latest version of the Editor (Version 1.3.4) 

 
What goes where?

firedocs-module.diff
https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lenya/contributions/2_0_X/modules/firedocs 

links-module.diff
https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lenya/branches/BRANCH_2_0_X

defaultfiredocs-example-content.diff
https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/lenya/contributions/2_0_X/pubs

In addition, the firedocs-1.2.4.xpi that ships with the module (see modules/firedocs/resources) needs to be replaced by the latest version available from firedocs.org

http://www.firedocs.org/files/firedocs-1.3.4.3.xpi
